0\\u0000(�\\u0002\\u0018\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000�\\u0004\\n`\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000�\\u0012(�\\u0001\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000J�\\u0000\\u0006\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000(�\\u0002\\u0018\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000�\\u0004\\n`\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000�\\u0012(�\\u0001\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000J�\\u0000\\u0006\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000(�\\u0002\\u0018\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000�\\u0004\\n`\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000�\\u0012(�\\u0001\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000J�\\u0000\\u0006\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000(�\\u0002\\u0018\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000�\\u0004\\n`\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000�\\u0012(�\\u0001\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000J�\\u0000\\u0006\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000(�\\u0002\\u0018\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000�\\u0004\\n`\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000�\\u0012(�\\u0001\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000J�\\u0000\\u0006\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000(�\\u0002\\u0018\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000�\\u0004\\n`\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000�\\u0012(�\\u0001\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000J�\\u0000\\u0006\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000(�\\u0002\\u0018\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000�\\u0004\\n`\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000�\\u0012(�\\u0001\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000J�\\u0000\\u0006\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000(�\\u0002\\u0018\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000�\\u0004\\n`\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000�\\u0012(�\\u0001\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000J�\\u0000\\u0006\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000(�\\u0002\\u0018\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000�\\u0004\\n`\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000�\\u0012(�\\u0001\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000J�\\u0000\\u0006\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000(�\\u0002\\u0018\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000�\\u0004\\n`\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000�\\u0012(�\\u0001\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000J�\\u0000\\u0006\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000(�\\u0002\\u0018\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000�\\u0004\\n`\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000�\\u0012(�\\u0001\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000J�\\u0000\\u0006\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000(�\\u0002\\u0018\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000�\\u0004\\n`\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000�\\u0012(�\\u0001\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000J�\\u0000\\u0006\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000(��\\u0001\\u0000\\u0000��i\\u0001��\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0006IDAT\\u0003\\u0000��M�C�7�\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000\\u0000IEND�B`�\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"file\": \"associations.html\",\n      \"data\": \"<!DOCTYPE html>\\n<html lang=\\\"en\\\">\\n<head>\\n  <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\">\\n  <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\">\\n  <title>Wild Lychee for Associations — AI-Powered Community Portal</title>\\n  <meta name=\\\"description\\\" content=\\\"A modern professional association portal with member directory, committee management, conference registration, and resource library. $5-20/mo flat. No per-member fees.\\\">\\n  <link rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" href=\\\"/css/marketing.css\\\">\\n</head>\\n<body>\\n\\n  <!-- ======== NAV ======== -->\\n  <nav class=\\\"nav\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"container nav__inner\\\">\\n      <a href=\\\"/\\\" class=\\\"nav__brand\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"nav__brand-icon\\\">&#127819;</span>\\n        Wild Lychee\\n      </a>\\n      <button class=\\\"nav__toggle\\\" id=\\\"nav-toggle\\\" aria-label=\\\"Menu\\\">&#9776;</button>\\n      <div class=\\\"nav__links\\\" id=\\\"nav-links\\\">\\n        <a href=\\\"/\\\" class=\\\"nav__link\\\">&larr; Back to Wild Lychee</a>\\n        <a href=\\\"#features\\\" class=\\\"nav__link\\\">Features</a>\\n        <a href=\\\"#pricing\\\" class=\\\"nav__link\\\">Pricing</a>\\n        <a href=\\\"https://github.com/kychee-com/wildlychee\\\" class=\\\"nav__link\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">GitHub</a>\\n        <a href=\\\"#demo-placeholder\\\" class=\\\"btn btn--primary btn--lg nav__cta\\\">Try the Demo</a>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </nav>\\n\\n  <!-- ======== HERO ======== -->\\n  <section class=\\\"hero section section--cream section--dotted\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"container hero__content\\\">\\n      <p class=\\\"t-overline mb-2\\\">Wild Lychee for Associations</p>\\n      <h1 class=\\\"t-display t-display--xl hero__headline\\\">\\n        Your association's member portal, built in 5 minutes.\\n      </h1>\\n      <p class=\\\"t-body--lg hero__sub\\\">\\n        Member directory with company profiles, committee management, conference registration, resource library, and membership tiers &mdash; all in one portal you actually own. No per-member fees. No lock-in. From <strong style=\\\"color:var(--ink)\\\">$5/mo</strong>.\\n      </p>\\n      <div class=\\\"hero__ctas\\\">\\n        <a href=\\\"#demo-placeholder\\\" class=\\\"btn btn--primary btn--lg\\\">Build Your Association Portal &rarr;</a>\\n        <a href=\\\"https://github.com/kychee-com/wildlychee\\\" class=\\\"btn btn--outline btn--lg\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Fork on GitHub</a>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"hero__aside\\\" aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\"></div>\\n  </section>\\n\\n  <!-- ======== FEATURES ======== -->\\n  <section class=\\\"section section--white\\\" id=\\\"features\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"container\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"section-header\\\">\\n        <p class=\\\"t-overline\\\">Built for Associations</p>\\n        <h2 class=\\\"t-display t-display--lg\\\">Everything your professional association needs.</h2>\\n        <p class=\\\"t-body--lg mt-2\\\">Six association-specific features, ready out of the box. Toggle them on with a config flag.</p>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"feature-grid\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"feature-card\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__icon\\\">&#128101;</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__name\\\">Member Directory</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__desc\\\">Searchable profiles with company names, titles, specialties, and contact info. Filter by region or expertise.</div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"feature-card\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__icon\\\">&#127963;&#65039;</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__name\\\">Committee Management</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__desc\\\">Working groups with chairs, members, meeting schedules, and shared documents. Track committee activities.</div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"feature-card\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__icon\\\">&#127915;</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__name\\\">Conference &amp; Events</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__desc\\\">Conference registration, session tracks, speaker bios, and attendee networking. Multi-day event support.</div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"feature-card\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__icon\\\">&#128218;</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__name\\\">Resource Library</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__desc\\\">Whitepapers, webinar recordings, industry reports, and best practices. Tier-gated access control.</div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"feature-card\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__icon\\\">&#127941;</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__name\\\">Membership Tiers</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__desc\\\">Fellow, Member, Associate, and Student tiers with different permissions, pricing, and resource access.</div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"feature-card\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__icon\\\">&#128202;</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__name\\\">Member Insights</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__desc\\\">AI-powered engagement analytics. Spot at-risk renewals, identify active contributors, and track growth.</div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </section>\\n\\n  <!-- ======== PRICING ======== -->\\n  <section class=\\\"section section--cream section--dotted\\\" id=\\\"pricing\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"container\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"section-header section-header--center\\\">\\n        <p class=\\\"t-overline\\\">Pricing</p>\\n        <h2 class=\\\"t-display t-display--lg\\\">Flat pricing. No per-member fees. Ever.</h2>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"plans-grid\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"plan-card\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__name\\\">DIY Template</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__price\\\">Free</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__price-sub\\\">+ $5&ndash;20/mo Run402 hosting</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__desc\\\">\\\"For developers and AI agents.\\\"</div>\\n          <ul class=\\\"plan-card__features\\\">\\n            <li>Full source code (open source)</li>\\n            <li>All features included</li>\\n            <li>Self-deploy to Run402</li>\\n            <li>Community support</li>\\n          </ul>\\n          <a href=\\\"https://github.com/kychee-com/wildlychee\\\" class=\\\"btn btn--outline\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Fork on GitHub</a>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div class=\\\"plan-card plan-card--featured\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__name\\\">Studio Build</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__price\\\">$29</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__price-sub\\\">one-time + $5&ndash;20/mo hosting</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__desc\\\">\\\"Tell us about your association. Live in 5 minutes.\\\"</div>\\n          <ul class=\\\"plan-card__features\\\">\\n            <li>AI investigates your existing site</li>\\n            <li>Guided interview &rarr; custom portal</li>\\n            <li>Brand colors, logo, content migrated</li>\\n            <li>Multi-language translation</li>\\n            <li>Chrome-verified deployment</li>\\n          </ul>\\n          <a href=\\\"#demo-placeholder\\\" class=\\\"btn btn--primary\\\">Build My Portal &rarr;</a>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div class=\\\"plan-card\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__name\\\">Lychee Pro</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__price\\\">$9&ndash;29/mo</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__price-sub\\\">ongoing, cancel anytime</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__desc\\\">\\\"Your portal evolves with you.\\\"</div>\\n          <ul class=\\\"plan-card__features\\\">\\n            <li>Ongoing AI customization agent</li>\\n            <li>Feature requests via chat</li>\\n            <li>Priority support</li>\\n            <li>Advanced analytics</li>\\n          </ul>\\n          <a href=\\\"#demo-placeholder\\\" class=\\\"btn btn--outline\\\">Learn More</a>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </section>\\n\\n  <!-- ======== FINAL CTA ======== -->\\n  <section class=\\\"section section--indigo final-cta\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"container\\\">\\n      <h2 class=\\\"t-display t-display--lg\\\">Stop paying per-member. Start owning your portal.</h2>\\n      <p class=\\\"t-body--lg\\\">Open source. Flat pricing. AI-powered. Yours forever.</p>\\n      <div class=\\\"final-cta__buttons\\\">\\n        <a href=\\\"#demo-placeholder\\\" class=\\\"btn btn--white btn--lg\\\">Build Your Association Portal &rarr;</a>\\n        <a href=\\\"https://github.com/kychee-com/wildlychee\\\" class=\\\"btn btn--outline btn--lg\\\" style=\\\"border-color:#fff;color:#fff\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Fork on GitHub</a>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </section>\\n\\n  <!-- ======== FOOTER ======== -->\\n  <footer class=\\\"footer\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"container\\\">\\n      <p>\\n        <strong>Wild Lychee</strong> is open source. Built on <a href=\\\"https://run402.com\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Run402</a>.\\n        &ensp;&middot;&ensp;\\n        <a href=\\\"https://github.com/kychee-com/wildlychee\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">GitHub</a>\\n        &ensp;&middot;&ensp;\\n        <a href=\\\"https://eagles.run402.com\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Eagles Demo</a>\\n      </p>\\n    </div>\\n  </footer>\\n\\n  <!-- Mobile nav toggle -->\\n  <script>\\n    document.getElementById('nav-toggle')?.addEventListener('click', () => {\\n      document.getElementById('nav-links')?.classList.toggle('open');\\n    });\\n  </script>\\n\\n</body>\\n</html>\\n\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"file\": \"capture-screenshots.sh\",\n      \"data\": \"#!/usr/bin/env zsh\\n# ============================================\\n# Capture showcase screenshots for marketing site\\n# Uses Chrome headless mode (no dependencies needed)\\n#\\n# Usage:\\n#   ./marketing/capture-screenshots.sh          # all sites\\n#   ./marketing/capture-screenshots.sh eagles   # just eagles\\n# ============================================\\n\\nset -e\\n\\nSCRIPT_DIR=\\\"${0:a:h}\\\"\\nASSETS_DIR=\\\"$SCRIPT_DIR/assets\\\"\\nmkdir -p \\\"$ASSETS_DIR\\\"\\n\\n# Find Chrome\\nif [[ -d \\\"/Applications/Google Chrome.app\\\" ]]; then\\n  CHROME=\\\"/Applications/Google Chrome.app/Contents/MacOS/Google Chrome\\\"\\nelif (( $+commands[google-chrome] )); then\\n  CHROME=\\\"google-chrome\\\"\\nelif (( $+commands[chromium] )); then\\n  CHROME=\\\"chromium\\\"\\nelse\\n  echo \\\"Chrome not found. Install Google Chrome.\\\"\\n  exit 1\\nfi\\n\\nWIDTH=1280\\nHEIGHT=800\\n\\ncapture() {\\n  local name=\\\"$1\\\"\\n  local url=\\\"$2\\\"\\n  local output=\\\"$ASSETS_DIR/screenshot-${name}.png\\\"\\n\\n  echo \\\"Capturing $name ($url)...\\\"\\n  # Use a small HTML page that navigates to the URL, waits for JS to render, then screenshots\\n  local tmphtml=$(mktemp /tmp/capture-XXXXXX.html)\\n  cat > \\\"$tmphtml\\\" <<HTMLEOF\\n<!DOCTYPE html>\\n<html><body><script>\\n  // Navigate and wait for content to load\\n  window.location = '$url';\\n</script></body></html>\\nHTMLEOF\\n\\n  # Use virtual-time-budget to let JS execute (5 seconds of simulated time)\\n  \\\"$CHROME\\\" \\\\\\n    --headless=new \\\\\\n    --disable-gpu \\\\\\n    --no-sandbox \\\\\\n    --hide-scrollbars \\\\\\n    --window-size=\\\"${WIDTH},${HEIGHT}\\\" \\\\\\n    --virtual-time-budget=8000 \\\\\\n    --screenshot=\\\"$output\\\" \\\\\\n    \\\"$url\\\" \\\\\\n    2>/dev/null\\n\\n  rm -f \\\"$tmphtml\\\"\\n\\n  if [[ -f \\\"$output\\\" ]]; then\\n    local size=$(du -h \\\"$output\\\" | cut -f1)\\n    echo \\\"  Saved: $output ($size)\\\"\\n  else\\n    echo \\\"  FAILED: $output not created\\\"\\n  fi\\n}\\n\\n# Showcase sites — add more as they're created\\ntypeset -A SITES\\nSITES=(\\n  eagles \\\"https://eagles.run402.com\\\"\\n  # yoga   \\\"https://yoga.run402.com\\\"\\n  # bookclub \\\"https://bookclub.run402.com\\\"\\n)\\n\\nif [[ -n \\\"$1\\\" ]]; then\\n  if [[ -n \\\"${SITES[$1]}\\\" ]]; then\\n    capture \\\"$1\\\" \\\"${SITES[$1]}\\\"\\n  else\\n    echo \\\"Unknown site: $1\\\"\\n    echo \\\"Available: ${(k)SITES}\\\"\\n    exit 1\\n  fi\\nelse\\n  for name url in \\\"${(@kv)SITES}\\\"; do\\n    capture \\\"$name\\\" \\\"$url\\\"\\n  done\\nfi\\n\\necho \\\"Done.\\\"\\n\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"file\": \"churches.html\",\n      \"data\": \"<!DOCTYPE html>\\n<html lang=\\\"en\\\">\\n<head>\\n  <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\">\\n  <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\">\\n  <title>Wild Lychee for Churches — AI-Powered Community Portal</title>\\n  <meta name=\\\"description\\\" content=\\\"A modern church portal with sermon archives, prayer requests, small group management, and multilingual support. $5-20/mo flat. No per-member fees.\\\">\\n  <link rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" href=\\\"/css/marketing.css\\\">\\n</head>\\n<body>\\n\\n  <!-- ======== NAV ======== -->\\n  <nav class=\\\"nav\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"container nav__inner\\\">\\n      <a href=\\\"/\\\" class=\\\"nav__brand\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"nav__brand-icon\\\">&#127819;</span>\\n        Wild Lychee\\n      </a>\\n      <button class=\\\"nav__toggle\\\" id=\\\"nav-toggle\\\" aria-label=\\\"Menu\\\">&#9776;</button>\\n      <div class=\\\"nav__links\\\" id=\\\"nav-links\\\">\\n        <a href=\\\"/\\\" class=\\\"nav__link\\\">&larr; Back to Wild Lychee</a>\\n        <a href=\\\"#features\\\" class=\\\"nav__link\\\">Features</a>\\n        <a href=\\\"#pricing\\\" class=\\\"nav__link\\\">Pricing</a>\\n        <a href=\\\"https://github.com/kychee-com/wildlychee\\\" class=\\\"nav__link\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">GitHub</a>\\n        <a href=\\\"#demo-placeholder\\\" class=\\\"btn btn--primary btn--lg nav__cta\\\">Try the Demo</a>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </nav>\\n\\n  <!-- ======== HERO ======== -->\\n  <section class=\\\"hero section section--cream section--dotted\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"container hero__content\\\">\\n      <p class=\\\"t-overline mb-2\\\">Wild Lychee for Churches</p>\\n      <h1 class=\\\"t-display t-display--xl hero__headline\\\">\\n        Your congregation deserves a modern home online.\\n      </h1>\\n      <p class=\\\"t-body--lg hero__sub\\\">\\n        Sermon archives, prayer requests, small group sign-ups, youth programs, and multilingual support &mdash; all in one portal your church actually owns. No per-member fees. No lock-in. From <strong style=\\\"color:var(--ink)\\\">$5/mo</strong>.\\n      </p>\\n      <div class=\\\"hero__ctas\\\">\\n        <a href=\\\"#demo-placeholder\\\" class=\\\"btn btn--primary btn--lg\\\">Build Your Church Portal &rarr;</a>\\n        <a href=\\\"https://github.com/kychee-com/wildlychee\\\" class=\\\"btn btn--outline btn--lg\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Fork on GitHub</a>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"hero__aside\\\" aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\"></div>\\n  </section>\\n\\n  <!-- ======== FEATURES ======== -->\\n  <section class=\\\"section section--white\\\" id=\\\"features\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"container\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"section-header\\\">\\n        <p class=\\\"t-overline\\\">Built for Churches</p>\\n        <h2 class=\\\"t-display t-display--lg\\\">Everything your congregation needs.</h2>\\n        <p class=\\\"t-body--lg mt-2\\\">Six church-specific features, ready out of the box. Toggle them on with a config flag.</p>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"feature-grid\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"feature-card\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__icon\\\">&#128214;</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__name\\\">Sermon Library</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__desc\\\">Archive sermons with audio, video, notes, and scripture references. Searchable by topic, speaker, or date.</div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"feature-card\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__icon\\\">&#128591;</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__name\\\">Prayer Requests</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__desc\\\">Members submit prayer requests with optional privacy settings. Congregation can respond with encouragement.</div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"feature-card\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__icon\\\">&#128101;</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__name\\\">Small Groups</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__desc\\\">Browse, join, and manage small groups with meeting times, locations, leaders, and member lists.</div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"feature-card\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__icon\\\">&#127925;</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__name\\\">Worship Team Resources</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__desc\\\">Sheet music, chord charts, set lists, and rehearsal schedules in a member-only resource library.</div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"feature-card\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__icon\\\">&#127760;</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__name\\\">Multi-Language Support</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__desc\\\">Serve your congregation in multiple languages. Built-in Portuguese/English support with AI-powered translation.</div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"feature-card\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__icon\\\">&#128197;</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__name\\\">Church Events</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__desc\\\">Sunday services, Bible studies, youth nights, potlucks &mdash; with RSVP tracking, reminders, and capacity limits.</div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </section>\\n\\n  <!-- ======== PRICING ======== -->\\n  <section class=\\\"section section--cream section--dotted\\\" id=\\\"pricing\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"container\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"section-header section-header--center\\\">\\n        <p class=\\\"t-overline\\\">Pricing</p>\\n        <h2 class=\\\"t-display t-display--lg\\\">Flat pricing. No per-member fees. Ever.</h2>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"plans-grid\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"plan-card\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__name\\\">DIY Template</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__price\\\">Free</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__price-sub\\\">+ $5&ndash;20/mo Run402 hosting</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__desc\\\">\\\"For developers and AI agents.\\\"</div>\\n          <ul class=\\\"plan-card__features\\\">\\n            <li>Full source code (open source)</li>\\n            <li>All features included</li>\\n            <li>Self-deploy to Run402</li>\\n            <li>Community support</li>\\n          </ul>\\n          <a href=\\\"https://github.com/kychee-com/wildlychee\\\" class=\\\"btn btn--outline\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Fork on GitHub</a>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div class=\\\"plan-card plan-card--featured\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__name\\\">Studio Build</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__price\\\">$29</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__price-sub\\\">one-time + $5&ndash;20/mo hosting</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__desc\\\">\\\"Tell us about your church. Live in 5 minutes.\\\"</div>\\n          <ul class=\\\"plan-card__features\\\">\\n            <li>AI investigates your existing site</li>\\n            <li>Guided interview &rarr; custom portal</li>\\n            <li>Brand colors, logo, content migrated</li>\\n            <li>Multi-language translation</li>\\n            <li>Chrome-verified deployment</li>\\n          </ul>\\n          <a href=\\\"#demo-placeholder\\\" class=\\\"btn btn--primary\\\">Build My Portal &rarr;</a>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div class=\\\"plan-card\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__name\\\">Lychee Pro</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__price\\\">$9&ndash;29/mo</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__price-sub\\\">ongoing, cancel anytime</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__desc\\\">\\\"Your portal evolves with you.\\\"</div>\\n          <ul class=\\\"plan-card__features\\\">\\n            <li>Ongoing AI customization agent</li>\\n            <li>Feature requests via chat</li>\\n            <li>Priority support</li>\\n            <li>Advanced analytics</li>\\n          </ul>\\n          <a href=\\\"#demo-placeholder\\\" class=\\\"btn btn--outline\\\">Learn More</a>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </section>\\n\\n  <!-- ======== FINAL CTA ======== -->\\n  <section class=\\\"section section--indigo final-cta\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"container\\\">\\n      <h2 class=\\\"t-display t-display--lg\\\">Give your congregation the home they deserve.</h2>\\n      <p class=\\\"t-body--lg\\\">Open source. Flat pricing. AI-powered. Yours forever.</p>\\n      <div class=\\\"final-cta__buttons\\\">\\n        <a href=\\\"#demo-placeholder\\\" class=\\\"btn btn--white btn--lg\\\">Build Your Church Portal &rarr;</a>\\n        <a href=\\\"https://github.com/kychee-com/wildlychee\\\" class=\\\"btn btn--outline btn--lg\\\" style=\\\"border-color:#fff;color:#fff\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Fork on GitHub</a>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </section>\\n\\n  <!-- ======== FOOTER ======== -->\\n  <footer class=\\\"footer\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"container\\\">\\n      <p>\\n        <strong>Wild Lychee</strong> is open source. Built on <a href=\\\"https://run402.com\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Run402</a>.\\n        &ensp;&middot;&ensp;\\n        <a href=\\\"https://github.com/kychee-com/wildlychee\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">GitHub</a>\\n        &ensp;&middot;&ensp;\\n        <a href=\\\"https://eagles.run402.com\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Eagles Demo</a>\\n      </p>\\n    </div>\\n  </footer>\\n\\n  <!-- Mobile nav toggle -->\\n  <script>\\n    document.getElementById('nav-toggle')?.addEventListener('click', () => {\\n      document.getElementById('nav-links')?.classList.toggle('open');\\n    });\\n  </script>\\n\\n</body>\\n</html>\\n\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"file\": \"css/marketing.css\",\n      \"data\": \"/* ============================================\\n   Wild Lychee Marketing — Editorial Indie\\n   ============================================ */\\n\\n@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,300;0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;0,9..40,600;0,9..40,700;1,9..40,400&family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&display=swap');\\n\\n/* --- Tokens --- */\\n:root {\\n  --ink: #1a1625;\\n  --ink-muted: #6b6680;\\n  --ink-subtle: #9994a8;\\n  --cream: #faf7f2;\\n  --cream-dark: #f0ebe3;\\n  --indigo: #4338ca;\\n  --indigo-light: #6366f1;\\n  --indigo-dark: #3730a3;\\n  --indigo-wash: #eef2ff;\\n  --coral: #f97316;\\n  --coral-light: #fb923c;\\n  --green: #16a34a;\\n  --green-wash: #dcfce7;\\n  --red-wash: #fee2e2;\\n  --red-muted: #b91c1c;\\n  --font-display: 'Instrument Serif', Georgia, serif;\\n  --font-body: 'DM Sans', -apple-system, sans-serif;\\n  --max-w: 72rem;\\n  --ease: cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);\\n}\\n\\n/* --- Reset --- */\\n*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\\n\\nhtml { scroll-behavior: smooth; }\\n\\nbody {\\n  font-family: var(--font-body);\\n  color: var(--ink);\\n  background: var(--cream);\\n  line-height: 1.65;\\n  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\\n  overflow-x: hidden;\\n}\\n\\nimg { max-width: 100%; display: block; }\\na { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }\\n\\n/* --- Layout --- */\\n.container {\\n  max-width: var(--max-w);\\n  margin: 0 auto;\\n  padding: 0 2rem;\\n}\\n\\n.section {\\n  padding: 7rem 0;\\n  position: relative;\\n}\\n\\n.section--cream { background: var(--cream); }\\n.section--white { background: #fff; }\\n.section--ink {\\n  background: var(--ink);\\n  color: #fff;\\n}\\n.section--indigo {\\n  background: var(--indigo);\\n  color: #fff;\\n}\\n\\n/* Dot-grid texture overlay */\\n.section--dotted::before {\\n  content: '';\\n  position: absolute;\\n  inset: 0;\\n  background-image: radial-gradient(circle, var(--ink) 0.5px, transparent 0.5px);\\n  background-size: 24px 24px;\\n  opacity: 0.04;\\n  pointer-events: none;\\n}\\n\\n/* Angled divider */\\n.slash {\\n  position: relative;\\n}\\n.slash::after {\\n  content: '';\\n  position: absolute;\\n  bottom: -2rem;\\n  left: 0;\\n  right: 0;\\n  height: 4rem;\\n  background: inherit;\\n  clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 30%, 0 100%);\\n  z-index: 2;\\n}\\n\\n/* --- Typography --- */\\n.t-display {\\n  font-family: var(--font-display);\\n  font-weight: 400;\\n  line-height: 1.1;\\n  letter-spacing: -0.02em;\\n}\\n\\n.t-display--xl { font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 6vw, 4.5rem); }\\n.t-display--lg { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); }\\n.t-display--md { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.25rem); }\\n\\n.t-overline {\\n  font-family: var(--font-body);\\n  font-size: 0.8125rem;\\n  font-weight: 600;\\n  letter-spacing: 0.1em;\\n  text-transform: uppercase;\\n  color: var(--indigo);\\n}\\n\\n.t-body { font-size: 1.125rem; color: var(--ink-muted); }\\n.t-body--lg { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--ink-muted); max-width: 38rem; }\\n.t-body--sm { font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--ink-muted); }\\n\\n.t-italic { font-style: italic; }\\n\\n/* --- Nav --- */\\n.nav {\\n  position: sticky;\\n  top: 0;\\n  z-index: 100;\\n  background: rgba(250, 247, 242, 0.9);\\n  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);\\n  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);\\n  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(26, 22, 37, 0.06);\\n  padding: 0.875rem 0;\\n}\\n\\n.nav__inner {\\n  display: flex;\\n  align-items: center;\\n  gap: 2rem;\\n}\\n\\n.nav__brand {\\n  font-family: var(--font-display);\\n  font-size: 1.375rem;\\n  color: var(--ink);\\n  display: flex;\\n  align-items: center;\\n  gap: 0.5rem;\\n  flex-shrink: 0;\\n}\\n\\n.nav__brand-icon {\\n  width: 1.75rem;\\n  height: 1.75rem;\\n  background: var(--indigo);\\n  border-radius: 6px;\\n  display: flex;\\n  align-items: center;\\n  justify-content: center;\\n  color: #fff;\\n  font-size: 1rem;\\n  transform: rotate(-6deg);\\n}\\n\\n.nav__links {\\n  display: flex;\\n  align-items: center;\\n  gap: 0.25rem;\\n  margin-left: auto;\\n}\\n\\n.nav__link {\\n  padding: 0.375rem 0.75rem;\\n  font-size: 0.875rem;\\n  font-weight: 500;\\n  color: var(--ink-muted);\\n  border-radius: 6px;\\n  transition: color 0.2s, background 0.2s;\\n}\\n\\n.nav__link:hover {\\n  color: var(--ink);\\n  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.04);\\n}\\n\\n.nav__cta {\\n  margin-left: 0.5rem;\\n}\\n\\n.nav__toggle {\\n  display: none;\\n  background: none;\\n  border: none;\\n  font-size: 1.5rem;\\n  cursor: pointer;\\n  color: var(--ink);\\n  padding: 0.25rem;\\n  margin-left: auto;\\n}\\n\\n/* --- Buttons --- */\\n.btn {\\n  display: inline-flex;\\n  align-items: center;\\n  gap: 0.5rem;\\n  padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;\\n  border-radius: 8px;\\n  font-family: var(--font-body);\\n  font-size: 0.9375rem;\\n  font-weight: 600;\\n  border: none;\\n  cursor: pointer;\\n  transition: transform 0.15s var(--ease), box-shadow 0.2s, background 0.2s;\\n  text-decoration: none;\\n}\\n.btn:active { transform: scale(0.97); }\\n\\n.btn--primary {\\n  background: var(--indigo);\\n  color: #fff;\\n  box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(67, 56, 202, 0.3);\\n}\\n.btn--primary:hover {\\n  background: var(--indigo-dark);\\n  box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(67, 56, 202, 0.3);\\n}\\n\\n.btn--outline {\\n  background: transparent;\\n  color: var(--ink);\\n  border: 1.5px solid var(--ink);\\n}\\n.btn--outline:hover {\\n  background: var(--ink);\\n  color: var(--cream);\\n}\\n\\n.btn--ghost {\\n  background: transparent;\\n  color: var(--indigo);\\n  padding: 0.75rem 1rem;\\n}\\n.btn--ghost:hover {\\n  background: var(--indigo-wash);\\n}\\n\\n.btn--coral {\\n  background: var(--coral);\\n  color: #fff;\\n}\\n.btn--coral:hover {\\n  background: var(--coral-light);\\n}\\n\\n.btn--white {\\n  background: #fff;\\n  color: var(--indigo);\\n}\\n.btn--white:hover {\\n  background: var(--cream);\\n}\\n\\n.btn--lg {\\n  padding: 1rem 2rem;\\n  font-size: 1.0625rem;\\n  border-radius: 10px;\\n}\\n\\n/* --- Hero --- */\\n.hero {\\n  padding: 8rem 0 6rem;\\n  position: relative;\\n}\\n\\n.hero__content {\\n  max-width: 48rem;\\n}\\n\\n.hero__headline {\\n  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\\n}\\n\\n.hero__headline em {\\n  color: var(--coral);\\n  font-style: normal;\\n  text-decoration: underline;\\n  text-decoration-color: var(--coral);\\n  text-underline-offset: 4px;\\n  text-decoration-thickness: 3px;\\n}\\n\\n.hero__sub {\\n  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;\\n}\\n\\n.hero__ctas {\\n  display: flex;\\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\\n  gap: 0.75rem;\\n}\\n\\n.hero__aside {\\n  position: absolute;\\n  right: 2rem;\\n  top: 50%;\\n  transform: translateY(-50%);\\n  width: 20rem;\\n  height: 20rem;\\n  background: var(--indigo-wash);\\n  border-radius: 50%;\\n  opacity: 0.5;\\n  filter: blur(60px);\\n  pointer-events: none;\\n}\\n\\n/* --- Problem cards --- */\\n.problem-grid {\\n  display: grid;\\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\\n  gap: 1.5rem;\\n  margin-bottom: 4rem;\\n}\\n\\n.problem-card {\\n  background: #fff;\\n  border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);\\n  border-radius: 12px;\\n  padding: 2rem;\\n  position: relative;\\n  overflow: hidden;\\n}\\n\\n.problem-card::before {\\n  content: '';\\n  position: absolute;\\n  top: 0;\\n  left: 0;\\n  right: 0;\\n  height: 3px;\\n  background: var(--red-muted);\\n  opacity: 0.6;\\n}\\n\\n.problem-card__name {\\n  font-weight: 700;\\n  font-size: 0.875rem;\\n  color: var(--red-muted);\\n  text-transform: uppercase;\\n  letter-spacing: 0.05em;\\n  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\\n}\\n\\n.problem-card__price {\\n  font-family: var(--font-display);\\n  font-size: 1.75rem;\\n  line-height: 1.2;\\n  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\\n}\\n\\n.problem-card__desc {\\n  font-size: 0.9375rem;\\n  color: var(--ink-muted);\\n  font-style: italic;\\n}\\n\\n.problem-transition {\\n  text-align: center;\\n  max-width: 36rem;\\n  margin: 0 auto;\\n}\\n\\n.problem-transition__what-if {\\n  font-family: var(--font-display);\\n  font-size: 2rem;\\n  font-style: italic;\\n  color: var(--indigo);\\n  margin-bottom: 1rem;\\n}\\n\\n/* --- Feature grid --- */\\n.feature-grid {\\n  display: grid;\\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);\\n  gap: 1.25rem;\\n}\\n\\n.feature-card {\\n  background: #fff;\\n  border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);\\n  border-radius: 12px;\\n  padding: 1.75rem;\\n  transition: transform 0.2s var(--ease), box-shadow 0.2s;\\n}\\n\\n.feature-card:hover {\\n  transform: translateY(-2px);\\n  box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);\\n}\\n\\n.feature-card__icon {\\n  font-size: 1.75rem;\\n  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\\n}\\n\\n.feature-card__name {\\n  font-weight: 700;\\n  font-size: 1rem;\\n  margin-bottom: 0.375rem;\\n}\\n\\n.feature-card__desc {\\n  font-size: 0.875rem;\\n  color: var(--ink-muted);\\n  line-height: 1.5;\\n}\\n\\n/* --- AI section --- */\\n.ai-section {\\n  background: var(--ink);\\n  color: #fff;\\n  position: relative;\\n  overflow: hidden;\\n}\\n\\n.ai-section .t-overline { color: var(--coral-light); }\\n.ai-section .t-body--lg { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }\\n\\n.ai-grid {\\n  display: grid;\\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\\n  gap: 1.25rem;\\n  margin-bottom: 2rem;\\n}\\n\\n.ai-card {\\n  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);\\n  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\\n  border-radius: 12px;\\n  padding: 1.75rem;\\n  transition: background 0.2s;\\n}\\n\\n.ai-card:hover {\\n  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\\n}\\n\\n.ai-card__icon {\\n  font-size: 1.5rem;\\n  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\\n}\\n\\n.ai-card__name {\\n  font-weight: 700;\\n  font-size: 1rem;\\n  margin-bottom: 0.375rem;\\n}\\n\\n.ai-card__desc {\\n  font-size: 0.875rem;\\n  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);\\n  line-height: 1.5;\\n}\\n\\n.ai-byok {\\n  display: inline-flex;\\n  align-items: center;\\n  gap: 0.5rem;\\n  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);\\n  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\\n  border-radius: 8px;\\n  padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;\\n  font-size: 0.875rem;\\n  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);\\n}\\n\\n/* Background glow */\\n.ai-section::before {\\n  content: '';\\n  position: absolute;\\n  top: -10rem;\\n  right: -10rem;\\n  width: 30rem;\\n  height: 30rem;\\n  background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--indigo) 0%, transparent 70%);\\n  opacity: 0.15;\\n  pointer-events: none;\\n}\\n\\n/* --- Showcase gallery --- */\\n.showcase-grid {\\n  display: grid;\\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\\n  gap: 1.5rem;\\n}\\n\\n.showcase-card {\\n  border-radius: 12px;\\n  overflow: hidden;\\n  border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\\n  background: #fff;\\n  transition: transform 0.2s var(--ease), box-shadow 0.2s;\\n}\\n\\n.showcase-card:hover {\\n  transform: translateY(-3px);\\n  box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\\n}\\n\\n.showcase-card__preview {\\n  height: 12rem;\\n  display: flex;\\n  align-items: center;\\n  justify-content: center;\\n  font-family: var(--font-display);\\n  font-size: 1.25rem;\\n  color: #fff;\\n  position: relative;\\n}\\n\\n.showcase-card__preview--eagles {\\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1b365d 0%, #2d4a7a 100%);\\n}\\n.showcase-card__preview--yoga {\\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #a78bfa 100%);\\n}\\n.showcase-card__preview--bookclub {\\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #065f46 0%, #059669 100%);\\n}\\n\\n.showcase-card__coming {\\n  position: absolute;\\n  top: 0.75rem;\\n  right: 0.75rem;\\n  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\\n  color: #fff;\\n  font-family: var(--font-body);\\n  font-size: 0.6875rem;\\n  font-weight: 600;\\n  padding: 0.25rem 0.625rem;\\n  border-radius: 99px;\\n  text-transform: uppercase;\\n  letter-spacing: 0.05em;\\n}\\n\\n.showcase-card__body {\\n  padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;\\n}\\n\\n.showcase-card__name {\\n  font-weight: 700;\\n  font-size: 1.0625rem;\\n  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;\\n}\\n\\n.showcase-card__niche {\\n  font-size: 0.8125rem;\\n  color: var(--ink-muted);\\n  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\\n}\\n\\n.showcase-card__link {\\n  font-size: 0.875rem;\\n  font-weight: 600;\\n  color: var(--indigo);\\n  display: inline-flex;\\n  align-items: center;\\n  gap: 0.25rem;\\n}\\n.showcase-card__link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }\\n\\n/* --- Pricing --- */\\n.pricing-comparison {\\n  overflow-x: auto;\\n  margin-bottom: 4rem;\\n  -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\\n}\\n\\n.pricing-table {\\n  width: 100%;\\n  border-collapse: collapse;\\n  font-size: 0.9375rem;\\n  min-width: 32rem;\\n}\\n\\n.pricing-table th {\\n  text-align: left;\\n  padding: 1rem 1.25rem;\\n  font-weight: 600;\\n  font-size: 0.8125rem;\\n  text-transform: uppercase;\\n  letter-spacing: 0.05em;\\n  color: var(--ink-muted);\\n  border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink);\\n}\\n\\n.pricing-table td {\\n  padding: 1rem 1.25rem;\\n  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);\\n}\\n\\n.pricing-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }\\n\\n.pricing-table__highlight {\\n  color: var(--indigo);\\n  font-weight: 700;\\n}\\n\\n.pricing-table__muted {\\n  color: var(--ink-subtle);\\n}\\n\\n.plans-grid {\\n  display: grid;\\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\\n  gap: 1.5rem;\\n}\\n\\n.plan-card {\\n  background: #fff;\\n  border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\\n  border-radius: 12px;\\n  padding: 2rem;\\n  display: flex;\\n  flex-direction: column;\\n}\\n\\n.plan-card--featured {\\n  border-color: var(--indigo);\\n  box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--indigo);\\n  position: relative;\\n}\\n\\n.plan-card--featured::before {\\n  content: 'Most Popular';\\n  position: absolute;\\n  top: -0.75rem;\\n  left: 1.5rem;\\n  background: var(--indigo);\\n  color: #fff;\\n  font-size: 0.6875rem;\\n  font-weight: 700;\\n  text-transform: uppercase;\\n  letter-spacing: 0.05em;\\n  padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;\\n  border-radius: 99px;\\n}\\n\\n.plan-card__name {\\n  font-family: var(--font-display);\\n  font-size: 1.5rem;\\n  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;\\n}\\n\\n.plan-card__price {\\n  font-size: 2rem;\\n  font-weight: 800;\\n  color: var(--indigo);\\n  margin-bottom: 0.125rem;\\n}\\n\\n.plan-card__price-sub {\\n  font-size: 0.8125rem;\\n  color: var(--ink-muted);\\n  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;\\n}\\n\\n.plan-card__desc {\\n  font-size: 0.9375rem;\\n  color: var(--ink-muted);\\n  font-style: italic;\\n  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\\n  flex: 1;\\n}\\n\\n.plan-card__features {\\n  list-style: none;\\n  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\\n}\\n\\n.plan-card__features li {\\n  font-size: 0.875rem;\\n  padding: 0.375rem 0;\\n  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.04);\\n  display: flex;\\n  align-items: center;\\n  gap: 0.5rem;\\n}\\n\\n.plan-card__features li::before {\\n  content: '\\\\2713';\\n  color: var(--green);\\n  font-weight: 700;\\n  font-size: 0.75rem;\\n}\\n\\n/* --- Niche cards --- */\\n.niche-grid {\\n  display: grid;\\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);\\n  gap: 1rem;\\n}\\n\\n.niche-card {\\n  background: #fff;\\n  border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);\\n  border-radius: 12px;\\n  padding: 1.5rem;\\n  text-align: center;\\n  transition: transform 0.2s var(--ease), box-shadow 0.2s;\\n}\\n\\n.niche-card:hover {\\n  transform: translateY(-2px);\\n  box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);\\n}\\n\\n.niche-card--disabled {\\n  opacity: 0.5;\\n  pointer-events: none;\\n}\\n\\n.niche-card__icon {\\n  font-size: 2rem;\\n  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\\n}\\n\\n.niche-card__name {\\n  font-weight: 700;\\n  font-size: 0.9375rem;\\n  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;\\n}\\n\\n.niche-card__sub {\\n  font-size: 0.75rem;\\n  color: var(--ink-subtle);\\n}\\n\\n/* --- Final CTA --- */\\n.final-cta {\\n  text-align: center;\\n}\\n\\n.final-cta .t-display--lg {\\n  color: #fff;\\n  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\\n}\\n\\n.final-cta .t-body--lg {\\n  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);\\n  margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;\\n}\\n\\n.final-cta__buttons {\\n  display: flex;\\n  justify-content: center;\\n  gap: 0.75rem;\\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\\n}\\n\\n/* --- Footer --- */\\n.footer {\\n  padding: 2.5rem 0;\\n  border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);\\n  text-align: center;\\n  font-size: 0.8125rem;\\n  color: var(--ink-muted);\\n}\\n\\n.footer a {\\n  color: var(--indigo);\\n  font-weight: 500;\\n}\\n.footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }\\n\\n/* --- Section header utility --- */\\n.section-header {\\n  margin-bottom: 3rem;\\n}\\n\\n.section-header--center {\\n  text-align: center;\\n  max-width: 40rem;\\n  margin-left: auto;\\n  margin-right: auto;\\n}\\n\\n.section-header .t-overline { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }\\n.section-header .t-display--lg { margin-bottom: 1rem; }\\n\\n/* --- Spacing utils --- */\\n.mb-1 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }\\n.mb-2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }\\n.mb-3 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }\\n.mb-4 { margin-bottom: 2rem; }\\n.mb-6 { margin-bottom: 3rem; }\\n.mt-2 { margin-top: 1rem; }\\n.mt-4 { margin-top: 2rem; }\\n\\n/* ============================================\\n   Responsive\\n   ============================================ */\\n\\n@media (max-width: 1024px) {\\n  .feature-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }\\n  .ai-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }\\n  .niche-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }\\n  .plans-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 28rem; }\\n}\\n\\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\\n  .section { padding: 4rem 0; }\\n  .container { padding: 0 1.25rem; }\\n\\n  /* Nav mobile */\\n  .nav__links { display: none; }\\n  .nav__links.open {\\n    display: flex;\\n    flex-direction: column;\\n    position: absolute;\\n    top: 100%;\\n    left: 0;\\n    right: 0;\\n    background: var(--cream);\\n    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);\\n    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;\\n    gap: 0.125rem;\\n  }\\n  .nav__links.open .nav__cta { margin-left: 0; margin-top: 0.5rem; }\\n  .nav__toggle { display: block; }\\n\\n  /* Hero */\\n  .hero { padding: 5rem 0 4rem; }\\n  .hero__aside { display: none; }\\n  .hero__ctas { flex-direction: column; }\\n  .hero__ctas .btn { justify-content: center; }\\n\\n  /* Grids */\\n  .problem-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\\n  .feature-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\\n  .ai-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\\n  .showcase-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\\n  .plans-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\\n  .niche-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }\\n\\n  .pricing-table { font-size: 0.8125rem; }\\n  .pricing-table th, .pricing-table td { padding: 0.75rem; }\\n}\\n\\n@media (max-width: 480px) {\\n  .niche-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\\n}\\n\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"file\": \"hoa.html\",\n      \"data\": \"<!DOCTYPE html>\\n<html lang=\\\"en\\\">\\n<head>\\n  <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\">\\n  <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\">\\n  <title>Wild Lychee for HOAs — AI-Powered Community Portal</title>\\n  <meta name=\\\"description\\\" content=\\\"A modern HOA portal with maintenance tracking, document archives, voting, and resident communication. $5-20/mo flat. No per-unit fees.\\\">\\n  <link rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" href=\\\"/css/marketing.css\\\">\\n</head>\\n<body>\\n\\n  <!-- ======== NAV ======== -->\\n  <nav class=\\\"nav\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"container nav__inner\\\">\\n      <a href=\\\"/\\\" class=\\\"nav__brand\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"nav__brand-icon\\\">&#127819;</span>\\n        Wild Lychee\\n      </a>\\n      <button class=\\\"nav__toggle\\\" id=\\\"nav-toggle\\\" aria-label=\\\"Menu\\\">&#9776;</button>\\n      <div class=\\\"nav__links\\\" id=\\\"nav-links\\\">\\n        <a href=\\\"/\\\" class=\\\"nav__link\\\">&larr; Back to Wild Lychee</a>\\n        <a href=\\\"#features\\\" class=\\\"nav__link\\\">Features</a>\\n        <a href=\\\"#pricing\\\" class=\\\"nav__link\\\">Pricing</a>\\n        <a href=\\\"https://github.com/kychee-com/wildlychee\\\" class=\\\"nav__link\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">GitHub</a>\\n        <a href=\\\"#demo-placeholder\\\" class=\\\"btn btn--primary btn--lg nav__cta\\\">Try the Demo</a>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </nav>\\n\\n  <!-- ======== HERO ======== -->\\n  <section class=\\\"hero section section--cream section--dotted\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"container hero__content\\\">\\n      <p class=\\\"t-overline mb-2\\\">Wild Lychee for HOAs</p>\\n      <h1 class=\\\"t-display t-display--xl hero__headline\\\">\\n        Your HOA deserves better than email chains and PDF attachments.\\n      </h1>\\n      <p class=\\\"t-body--lg hero__sub\\\">\\n        Maintenance requests, document archives, voting, announcements, and resident communication &mdash; all in one portal your board actually controls. No per-unit fees. No lock-in. From <strong style=\\\"color:var(--ink)\\\">$5/mo</strong>.\\n      </p>\\n      <div class=\\\"hero__ctas\\\">\\n        <a href=\\\"#demo-placeholder\\\" class=\\\"btn btn--primary btn--lg\\\">Build Your HOA Portal &rarr;</a>\\n        <a href=\\\"https://github.com/kychee-com/wildlychee\\\" class=\\\"btn btn--outline btn--lg\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Fork on GitHub</a>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"hero__aside\\\" aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\"></div>\\n  </section>\\n\\n  <!-- ======== FEATURES ======== -->\\n  <section class=\\\"section section--white\\\" id=\\\"features\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"container\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"section-header\\\">\\n        <p class=\\\"t-overline\\\">Built for HOAs</p>\\n        <h2 class=\\\"t-display t-display--lg\\\">Everything your community association needs.</h2>\\n        <p class=\\\"t-body--lg mt-2\\\">Six HOA-specific features, ready out of the box. Toggle them on with a config flag.</p>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"feature-grid\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"feature-card\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__icon\\\">&#128295;</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__name\\\">Maintenance Requests</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__desc\\\">Residents submit issues with photos and descriptions. Board tracks status from open to resolved.</div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"feature-card\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__icon\\\">&#128196;</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__name\\\">Document Archive</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__desc\\\">CC&amp;Rs, meeting minutes, financial reports, and bylaws &mdash; organized, searchable, and always accessible.</div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"feature-card\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__icon\\\">&#9989;</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__name\\\">Voting &amp; Polls</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__desc\\\">Run board elections, budget approvals, and community polls with transparent results and audit trails.</div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"feature-card\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__icon\\\">&#128100;</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__name\\\">Resident &amp; Board Roles</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__desc\\\">Separate permissions for residents, board members, and property managers. Everyone sees what they need.</div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"feature-card\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__icon\\\">&#128247;</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__name\\\">Issue Submission</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__desc\\\">Report problems with photo uploads, location details, and priority levels. Track resolution in real time.</div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"feature-card\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__icon\\\">&#128226;</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__name\\\">Announcement Wall</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"feature-card__desc\\\">Board posts announcements with reactions and comments. Pin important notices. Replace those paper flyers.</div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </section>\\n\\n  <!-- ======== PRICING ======== -->\\n  <section class=\\\"section section--cream section--dotted\\\" id=\\\"pricing\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"container\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"section-header section-header--center\\\">\\n        <p class=\\\"t-overline\\\">Pricing</p>\\n        <h2 class=\\\"t-display t-display--lg\\\">Flat pricing. No per-unit fees. Ever.</h2>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"plans-grid\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"plan-card\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__name\\\">DIY Template</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__price\\\">Free</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__price-sub\\\">+ $5&ndash;20/mo Run402 hosting</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__desc\\\">\\\"For developers and AI agents.\\\"</div>\\n          <ul class=\\\"plan-card__features\\\">\\n            <li>Full source code (open source)</li>\\n            <li>All features included</li>\\n            <li>Self-deploy to Run402</li>\\n            <li>Community support</li>\\n          </ul>\\n          <a href=\\\"https://github.com/kychee-com/wildlychee\\\" class=\\\"btn btn--outline\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Fork on GitHub</a>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div class=\\\"plan-card plan-card--featured\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__name\\\">Studio Build</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__price\\\">$29</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__price-sub\\\">one-time + $5&ndash;20/mo hosting</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__desc\\\">\\\"Tell us about your HOA. Live in 5 minutes.\\\"</div>\\n          <ul class=\\\"plan-card__features\\\">\\n            <li>AI investigates your existing site</li>\\n            <li>Guided interview &rarr; custom portal</li>\\n            <li>Brand colors, logo, content migrated</li>\\n            <li>Multi-language translation</li>\\n            <li>Chrome-verified deployment</li>\\n          </ul>\\n          <a href=\\\"#demo-placeholder\\\" class=\\\"btn btn--primary\\\">Build My Portal &rarr;</a>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div class=\\\"plan-card\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__name\\\">Lychee Pro</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__price\\\">$9&ndash;29/mo</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__price-sub\\\">ongoing, cancel anytime</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"plan-card__desc\\\">\\\"Your portal evolves with you.\\\"</div>\\n          <ul class=\\\"plan-card__features\\\">\\n            <li>Ongoing AI customization agent</li>\\n            <li>Feature requests via chat</li>\\n            <li>Priority support</li>\\n            <li>Advanced analytics</li>\\n          </ul>\\n          <a href=\\\"#demo-placeholder\\\" class=\\\"btn btn--outline\\\">Learn More</a>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </section>\\n\\n  <!-- ======== FINAL CTA ======== -->\\n  <section class=\\\"section section--indigo final-cta\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"container\\\">\\n      <h2 class=\\\"t-display t-display--lg\\\">Ditch the email chains. Give your HOA a real portal.</h2>\\n      <p class=\\\"t-body--lg\\\">Open source. Flat pricing. AI-powered. Yours forever.</p>\\n      <div class=\\\"final-cta__buttons\\\">\\n        <a href=\\\"#demo-placeholder\\\" class=\\\"btn btn--white btn--lg\\\">Build Your HOA Portal &rarr;</a>\\n        <a href=\\\"https://github.com/kychee-com/wildlychee\\\" class=\\\"btn btn--outline btn--lg\\\" style=\\\"border-color:#fff;color:#fff\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Fork on GitHub</a>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </section>\\n\\n  <!-- ======== FOOTER ======== -->\\n  <footer class=\\\"footer\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"container\\\">\\n      <p>\\n        <strong>Wild Lychee</strong> is open source. Built on <a href=\\\"https://run402.com\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Run402</